The paper discusses research performance in advanced technology and basic medical research, which are interdisciplinary fields that involve computer science. The analysis of ERC publications suggests that changes in research policy are needed to improve research performance, which is relevant to the fields of digital libraries (cs.DL), distributed and parallel computing (cs.DC), information retrieval (cs.IR), cryptography and security (cs.CR), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
